{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_19051.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story08","nameNarration":"Iroha","narration":"We ended up searching for the missing Rikki.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"Tsuruno and Hinano headed off to look for her."},{"narration":"Emily went to enlist more people to help."},{"narration":"And I..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":301,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Iroha","nameLeft":"Mitama","nameRight":"Iroha","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"*Sigh*"},{"chara":[{"id":100100,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"(This is the entrance, but there's no sign  @of Mitama.)"},{"textBg":"shout","textLeft":"Irohaaa!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":1}],"textCenter":"[chara:100100:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Eek!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":100100,"pos":2}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"Hi there!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}],"textRight":"Geeze, you scared me!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100}],"textRight":"Don't shout at me from behind like that!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"Oh, but when scaring someone, isn't it@common to do it from behind?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101700}],"textLeft":"And you're the one who popped out in front@of me!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}],"textRight":"Huh? Oh, I guess you're right."},{"chara":[{"id":101700,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"I certainly am! Honestly."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":301}],"textRight":"Well, I'm sorry about..."},{"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}],"textRight":"Hang on! That's still no excuse to scare@me!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"Oh that? I just thought it would be fun!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700}],"textLeft":"Anyway, your eyes were darting everywhere.@Are you looking for someone?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100}],"textRight":"Oh, right! I was looking for you!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":101700}],"textLeft":"Who, me?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}],"textRight":"Yes. You see..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"textLeft":"So that's what happened...","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}],"textRight":"I was wondering if you might know something@about what's going on."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"Well, one thing's for sure. That's a fake."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}],"textRight":"Huh?! You're so positive."},{"chara":[{"id":101700}],"textLeft":"Why should I beat around the bush?"},{"chara":[{"id":101700,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Besides, we're running out of time!"},{"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":400}],"textRight":"We are?!"},{"chara":[{"id":101700}],"textLeft":"Yes..."},{"chara":[{"id":101700}],"textLeft":"Rika said she was going deep into the@mirror, didn't she?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}],"textRight":"That's right! She did!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"Which means..."},{"chara":[{"id":101700}],"textLeft":"She may have spent too long staring into the@mirrors."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}],"textRight":"What?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101700,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"She may have glimpsed the abyss that lies@in the depths of Mirrors."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100}],"textRight":"An abyss? [chara:100100:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:100100:cheek_0][chara:100100:face_mtn_ex_030.exp.json][chara:100100:lipSynch_1]What does that mean?"},{"chara":[{"id":101700}],"textLeft":"I've told you enough for now."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":401}],"textRight":"You can't be serious!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"We can talk more later."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400}],"textRight":"But!"},{"chara":[{"id":101700}],"textLeft":"You had better hurry and get back in there.@Don't you remember what I just said?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101700}],"textLeft":"We're running out of time!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}],"textRight":"Right..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"I'll tell you what I know next time."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101700}],"textLeft":"For now you should go back."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}],"textRight":"Um, well... I..."},{"chara":[{"id":101700,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"Hurry!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}],"textRight":"O-okay!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":100100}]},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101700,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101700}],"textLeft":"See you again soon, Iroha."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}